With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

snippet.description:

But now, the former India skipper has turned heads for something very different: wielding guns in an action-packed teaser alongside Bollywood star R Madhavan.

What came as a big surprise on August 7, Madhavan surprised fans by dropping the clip of his upcoming project The Chase, directed by Vasan Bala. The teaser shows both Madhavan and Dhoni dressed in tactical black gear, complete with bulletproof vests and sunglasses, stepping into character as officers on a high-stakes mission. The sight of “Captain Cool” in an action sequence sent social media into overdrive, with fans already dubbing it Dhoni’s big-screen debut.
